cast.overview: American expat Mickey Pearson has built a highly profitable marijuana empire in London. When word gets out that he’s looking to cash out of the business forever it triggers plots, schemes, bribery and blackmail in an attempt to steal his domain out from under him.
cast.title: The Gentlemen

also_known_as: ブリタニー・アシュワース
details.biography:
Brittany Ashworth is an English actress. She is known for playing Alex Ratcliffe in the 2014 film Mrs Ratcliffe's Revolution. She starred as Juliette in the 2017 apocalyptic thriller film Hostile [fr], and as Kelly in the 2022 direct-to-video film The Ledge.

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
